#| "The mass of an element is the avarage mass of all isotopes in relation to "
#| "their percentage."
msgid ""
"The mass of an element is the average mass of all isotopes in relation to "
"their percentage."
msgstr ""
"Et grundstofs masse er gennemsnitsmassen for alle isotoper i forhold til "
"deres procent."

